T02D1761:252a-1: shr'i ma h'a k'a la s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02D1761:252a-3: dpal nag po chen po'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02D1761:252a-4: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1761:252a-5: bla ma la gus snying rjer ldan //
T02D1761:252a-6: tshul khrims sogs ldan bsdu dngos bzhis //
T02D1761:252a-7: sems can don byed brtson 'grus ldan //
T02D1761:252a-8: rtag tu bsgrub la dga' ba yis //
T02D1761:252a-9: slob dpon la smod bstan la sdang //
T02D1761:252a-10: dam tshig la 'phya mtshams med byed //
T02D1761:252a-11: de rnams bsgral bar bya ba yin //
T02D1761:252a-12: gzhan du dam tshig nyams par 'gyur //
T02D1761:252a-13: dang por bdag nyid yi dam lha //
T02D1761:252a-14: rim pa thams cad rdzogs bsgoms la //
T02D1761:252a-15: bstan pa bsrung phyir nag po mchod //
T02D1761:252a-16: brag steng dkyil 'khor gru gsum gnas //
T02D1761:252a-17: h'um skyes 'bar ba nag po che //
T02D1761:252a-18: gri dang ka p'a la lag na 'dzin //
T02D1761:252a-19: mgo bo'i phreng bas do shal byas //
T02D1761:252a-20: mche gtsigs gzugs thung gzi brjid che //
T02D1761:252a-21: kha nas khrag 'dzag khros tsam na //
T02D1761:252a-22: rang gi yan lag sha gcod byed //
T02D1761:252a-23: khrag gi rgyun yang 'dzag par byed //
T02D1761:252a-24: dkon mchog gsum khro bla ma brnyas //
T02D1761:252a-25: mtshams med la sogs byed rnams kyi //
T02D1761:252a-26: de rnams mgo nas til tsam za //
T02D1761:252a-27: de ltar gsal bar byas nas ni //
T02D1761:252a-28: rang gi gnas nas spyan 'dren bya ;
T02D1761:252a-29: / rdo rje 'chang gi spyan snga ru //
T02D1761:252a-30: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas ltar //
T02D1761:252a-31: byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas 'di ru //
T02D1761:252a-32: drag po'i las la spyan 'dren na //
T02D1761:252a-33: myur du 'ongs nas de la thim //
T02D1761:252a-34: mon sran gre'u dang 'dzam bu'i ti //
T02D1761:252a-35: me tog bdug spos sha lnga dang //
T02D1761:252a-36: bdud rtsi lnga sbyar gtor ma sbyin //
T02D1761:252a-37: aom ma h'a k'a l'a ya sh'a sa no ba h'a ri ne /
T02D1761:252a-38: ae sh'a pashtsi ma k'a lo aa yam ai dam /
T02D1761:252a-39: ratna tra y'a y'a pa ka ri n'am /
T02D1761:252a-40: ya di pra t'i dzny'a sma ra si ta d'a ai dam dusht'am kha kha kh'a hi kh'a hi /
T02D1761:252a-47: da ni me ka na m'a ra ya h'um phat /
T02D1761:252a-48: nag po khyod kyis sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan
T02D1761:252a-49: sngar khas blangs pa bzhin du ngas ci bcol pa'i
T02D1761:252a-50: las gyis shig / de ltar ma byas na mgo
T02D1761:252a-51: aardza ka'i dog pa ltar 'gas so //
T02D1761:252a-55: h'um srin po'i gzugs kyis gdug pa can //
T02D1761:252b-0: tshar gcod byang chub @252b sems dpa' ste //
T02D1761:252b-1: grong khyer sum brtsegs 'jig byed pa //
T02D1761:252b-2: gtum po khyod la bdag bstod do //
T02D1761:252b-3: mdog nag gzugs thung gzi brjid can //
T02D1761:252b-4: gdug pa tshar gcod gri gug g-yas //
T02D1761:252b-5: g-yon pa gdug pa'i khrag bkang snod //
T02D1761:252b-6: thod phreng can la bdag bstod do //
T02D1761:252b-7: khros pas zhabs brdabs sa gzhi g-yos //
T02D1761:252b-8: 'jigs pa'i gad mos ri rab bsgyel //
T02D1761:252b-9: dam tshig nyams pa'i snyid 'byin pa //
T02D1761:252b-10: dam tshig can la bdag bstod do //
T02D1761:252b-12: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
T02D1761:252b-13: bstan pa bsrung bar sems bskyed pa //
T02D1761:252b-14: nag po khyod ni yin pa ste //
T02D1761:252b-15: gdug pa tshar gcod 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02D1761:252b-16: ral pa nag po gyen du g-yengs //
T02D1761:252b-17: steng gi lha tshogs 'jigs par byed //
T02D1761:252b-18: spyan bgrad ljags 'dril bar gyi lha gdon sdigs //
T02D1761:252b-19: g-yas pa gri gug gnod sems can la sdang //
T02D1761:252b-20: g-yon pas thod pa gnod sems khrag bkang gsol //
T02D1761:252b-21: zhabs brdabs gnod sems can gyi lus la nyed //
T02D1761:252b-22: gang zhig dkon mchog gsum khro dang //
T02D1761:252b-23: bla ma brnyas byed sems can 'tshe //
T02D1761:252b-24: bdag gis bsgo ba kun khug la //
T02D1761:252b-25: ling+ga 'di la myur du chug /'di yi sha zo khrag la 'thung //
T02D1761:252b-26: rus pa klad pa nang grol zo //
T02D1761:252b-27: rigs rgyud rtsad nas chod la shog / mdza' ba
T02D1761:252b-28: kun dang phrol la shog / bdag gis bsgo ba
T02D1761:252b-29: ma nyan na // nag po khyod ni nyams par 'gyur //
T02D1761:252b-31: gong gi sngags sam yang na /
T02D1761:252b-32: aom ma h'a k'a la che ge mo h'um phat /
T02D1761:252b-34: de nas sbyor ba bshad bya ba //
T02D1761:252b-35: tsha ba gsum la gzugs brnyan bya ;
T02D1761:252b-36: / dug dang ske tshe lan tshv'a dang //
T02D1761:252b-37: tshv'a gsum smyo byed srin lag khrag / gro gar
T02D1761:252b-38: sngags spel snying gar gzhug / gdug pa'i tsher mas

T02D1761:252b-44: klu yod gnas su'ang gang bsgo 'grub //

T02D1761:253a-8: des ni the tshom med par 'grub //

T02D1761:253a-13: bzlas gtor ser sogs 'chad par byed //
T02D1761:253a-14: nag po sngags kyi sbyor ba yi //
